 />\n<br />\n最有效既降溫.,<br />\n請換DESKTOP, <br />\n一係自行上水冷俾部NB (整泥做咩???)<br />\n<br />\n同埋, 長期高溫對DESKTOP CPU可能有傷,<br />\nNB, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2010 人生第一部NB, ASUS 玩到98度, KEEP左3年,<br />\n依家仲用到"},{"pid":"bbc16603db8aeae70f9604a3e7d9cb0374e60020","tid":935020,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"98度對cpu黎講好小兒科<br />\n你驚供電頂唔順好過"},{"pid":"db39f8699c9311ee467e344506c2a093fdf89038","tid":935020,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc16603db8aeae70f9604a3e7d9cb0374e60020","tid":935020,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"98度對cpu黎講好小兒科<br />\n你驚供電頂唔順好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"set 110度嘅人路過...<br />\nCPU呢D非活動組件其實好耐熱嘅"},{"pid":"42e1412cfab9f7ffe9489a3131046f6e7ce51d5c","tid":935020,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"macbook pro 長期9x度 bootcamp打機5年仲冇病冇痛 一次都未整過"},{"pid":"288ef797885f7fbf703ed1c73f3d1724fbd83934","tid":935020,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"自己diy上水冷咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badb6dfe12577017a0b43513bd5671bad6e2dfda","tid":935020,"uid":117753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eac33514411b8a31e1454e49ab0fffcdc540fb9","tid":935020,"uid":43070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T18:45:32.000Z","msg":"如果notebook底墊nb cooler都無用就要換thermal plate<br />\n<br />\n再唔係裝個intel xtu 改低dd電壓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"成日聽人話8550U改得唔多-90.8mV已經好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 散熱墊諗得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ec17ade537fd7262bada977ec1e0059ae44e2a","tid":935020,"uid":117753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote